{
  "_comment": "Codex Hooks 模板：使用社区方案 dcg（Destructive Command Guard）作为默认硬层防护。Codex 当前 PreToolUse matcher 按工具名匹配 Bash，无法只匹配危险命令；因此本模板指向轻量过滤器，只有命令看起来高危时才调用 dcg 本体。",
  "_doc": "https://developers.openai.com/codex/hooks",
  "_dcg": "https://github.com/Dicklesworthstone/destructive_command_guard",
  "hooks": {
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "__DCG_HOOK_COMMAND__",
            "timeout": 10
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
